page.title: 13SPARE TIME ACTIVITIES (25+)
page.content: Most people of this age group seem to spend their spare time gardening.The people as a whole enjoy family trips as well as holidays if they have any money spare.The majority of people who have jobs are men.A lot of the people who have pets like cats and dogs with a few exceptions. Nearly all the people over 25 are married.Quite a few of them go out to clubs and meals and the small minority help run the youth club.Most of the married community have children.People in Raunds are very keen on music.A lot of the people enjoy other peoples company.About 70% of the public dislike housework.
